# Forecast API Test Endpoints
# Test the C# backend that calls Python ML service

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5228
@forecastUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/forecasts

### Health Check - Forecast Service
GET {{forecastUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### Demand Forecast - Basic test
POST {{forecastUrl}}/demand
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "week": "17/01/11",
    "store_id": 8091,
    "sku_id": 216418,
    "base_price": 111.8625,
    "total_price": 99.0375,
    "is_featured_sku": 0,
    "is_display_sku": 0
}

### Demand Forecast - Without total_price (should default to base_price)
POST {{forecastUrl}}/demand
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "week": "17/01/11",
    "store_id": 8091,
    "sku_id": 216418,
    "base_price": 111.8625,
